<div class="frontpage">
	<div class="row">
		<div class="col-md-12 text-center">
			<h1>Eisenhower Matrix App</h1>
			<br>
			<p><i>"I have two kinds of problems, the urgent and the important. The urgent are not important, and the important are never urgent."</i> <br> - Dwight Eisenhower</p>
			<p>This free web app allows you to manage tasks using the <a target="_blank" href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Time_management#The_Eisenhower_Method"> Eisenhower Matrix</a> principle.</p>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="row demo">
			<div class="col-md-8 col-md-offset-2">
				<div class="col-md-6">
					<div class="col-md-12 frontcard text-center important urgent">
						<span class="glyphicon glyphicon-time"></span>
						<span class="glyphicon glyphicon-exclamation-sign"></span>
						<p>Important and urgent tasks should be done right now.</p>
						<p>E.g. deadlines, problems, crisis.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="col-md-6">
					<div class="col-md-12 frontcard text-center important">
						<span class="glyphicon glyphicon-time"></span>
						<span class="glyphicon glyphicon-exclamation-sign"></span>
						<p>Important but not urgent tasks should be planned in.</p>
						<p>E.g. relationships, planning, recreation.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="row">
			<div class="col-md-8 col-md-offset-2">
				<div class="col-md-6">
					<div class="col-md-12 frontcard text-center urgent">
						<span class="glyphicon glyphicon-time"></span>
						<span class="glyphicon glyphicon-exclamation-sign"></span>
						<p>Not important but urgent tasks should be delegated where possible.</p>
						<p>E.g. interruptions, useless meetings</p>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="col-md-6">
					<div class="col-md-12 frontcard text-center">
						<span class="glyphicon glyphicon-time"></span>
						<span class="glyphicon glyphicon-exclamation-sign"></span>
						<p>Not important and not urgent urgent tasks should be deleted where possible.</p>
						<p>E.g. time wasters, trivial matters</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>